Package net.bitnine.agensgraph.ext.agtype

Class AgtypeMapBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.bitnine.agensgraph.ext.agtype.AgtypeMapBuilder
  • public class AgtypeMapBuilder
extends Object
    A builder for creating an AgtypeMap object. This class initializes a AgtypeMap object, provides methods to add name/value pairs and return the resulting object. The methods in this class can be chained to add multiple name/value pairs to the AgtypeMap.
    Since:
    0.0.1
    See Also:
    AgtypeMap, Agtype
